        "subject": "LU-577 tests: REPLAY_SINGLE test_70b failed in rundbench",
        "message": "LU-577 tests: REPLAY_SINGLE test_70b failed in rundbench\n\nWhen I run \"ACC_SM_ONLY=REPLAY_SINGLE NAME=my_config sh\nacceptance-small.sh\", test 70b failed if my $MOUNT is not\n/mnt/lustre.\n\nThe $MOUNT variable was set in my_config script and exported. The\nvariable was picked up in replay-single.sh, but failed to pass on\nto rundbench.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jay J Lan <jay.j.lan@nasa.gov>\nChange-Id: I03688b4bb282bce6610559bc173a368c088ed1dc\n"
